executable file to be run to manage guests (called from hypervisor definition)
  create [[low] high] [more here?] (default: low:0 high:1)
    create a number of guests with the given parameters
  start [[low] high] (default: low:0 high:max)
    start the guests within the given id range
  stop [[low] high] (default: low:0 high:max)
    stop the guests within the given id range
  clean [[low] high] (default: low:0 high:max)
    clean the guests within the given id range

naming convention:
  hypervisor-name_storage-technology
  e.g. "xen_dd-file"
